ygData.messageBody:
I don't have wolf form. I just got my character to lvl 11 last night. She's
a Wizard. And to be honest, I don't know where to turn the belts in.
I have a ton or orc picks though....
I can probaly turn those babies in for alot of xp. maybe even some
faction...
The commons residents now con amiable to me...
luv,
-Su
